article.description: — Hunter McIntosh had 13 points as eighth-seeded Elon romped past ninth-seeded Towson 69-48 in the first round of the Colonial Conference Tourney on Saturday.
article.headline: McIntosh has 13, Elon tops Towson 69-48 in CAA tourney
article.linkText: McIntosh has 13, Elon tops Towson 69-48 in CAA tourney
article.story: HARRISONBURG, Va. -- — Hunter McIntosh had 13 points as eighth-seeded Elon romped past ninth-seeded Towson 69-48 in the first round of the Colonial Conference Tourney on Saturday. The Phoenix face league champion James Madison in the quarterfinals on Sunday. Darius Burford had 11 points for Elon (8-8). Hunter Woods added eight rebounds. Nicolas Timberlake had 14 points for the Tigers (4-14). ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
